	"skyRotation": 0,
	"skyType": 0,
	"startPosition": "The start position is anywhere in the shooting area.\r\nHandgun is loaded and holstered, wrists below belt.\r\nPCC loaded with stock touching belt.",
	"procedure": "On the audible start signal, engage all targets from within the shooting area.\r\n\r\nPopper 2 activates the Max Trap which remains visible at rest.",
